<h2><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Kansas City, KS.</span></h2>
<p>Hosted by<span class="fcg"> <a id="js_14" class="profileLink" href="https://www.facebook.com/KCKCopBlock" data-ft="{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;k&quot;}" data-hovercard="/ajax/hovercard/page.php?id=297273257076773&amp;extragetparams=%7B%22directed_target_id%22%3A143037152533300%7D">KCK Cop Block</a></span></p>
