<li><strong>Friday, July 18 at 12:00pm (CDT)</strong></li>
<li><span class="_6s_"><span class="_6s_"><span class="_5ini fsm fwn fcg"><a class="_5inl" href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Wyandotte-County-Courthouse/144788882247839" data-hovercard="/ajax/hovercard/page.php?id=144788882247839">Wyandotte County Courthouse</a> <span class="_6s_"><span class="_5ini fsm fwn fcg"><span class="_6s_"><span class="_5inl" data-hover="tooltip" data-tooltip-display="overflow">(click for</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>
