<h2><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Portland, OR.</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>FaceBook event page: <span class="_6lc fwb"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/824266020957943/?ref=4" data-ft="{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;q&quot;}">Across the states: Chalking against police violence and police impunity</a></span></li>
<li><strong>Friday, July 18 at 4:30pm (PDT)</strong></li>
<li><span class="_6s_"><span class="_5inl" data-hover="tooltip" data-tooltip-display="overflow">NW 8th and Burnside</span></span></li>
<li>Portland, Oregon</li>
</ul>
