		<title>More Cops Does Not Mean More Justice For Las Vegas &#8211; Submitted by Adam Sanacore</title>
		<link>http://nvcopblock.org/1281/morecopsnotmorejustice/</link>
		<comments>http://nvcopblock.org/1281/morecopsnotmorejustice/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2014 10:25:47 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[NVCopBlock.org]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Commentary]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[CopBlock.org]]></category>
